1. Withdraw transaction happy flow
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Automatic transition to the dashboard page occurs.
Step definition:
- Click "Withdraw" in the left menu bar.
- Click "New Withdraw" in the drop-down menu.
- Copy text in the "Transaction reference" field.
- Select "1" in the "Withdraw amount" field.
- Select option "Poodle White" in the "Puppy" field.
- Click "Confirm" button.
Expexted result:
- Automatic transition to the page "Withdraw Transaction List".
- New transaction with previously copied text in the "Transaction Reference" field.

2. Withdraw transaction with empty fields
Pre-condition:
- Navigate to Puppy Bank login page.
- Login as admin.
- Automatic transition to the dashboard page occurs.
Step definition:
- Click "Withdraw" in the left menu bar.
- Click "New Withdraw" in the drop-down menu.
- Check "Withdraw amount" field is empty.
- Don't select option in the "Puppy" field.
- Click "Confirm" button.
Expexted result:
- We stayed on the "Withdraw Transaction" page.

